{"tid":859034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屢傳死訊害家人擔心 洪卓立開騷哭成淚人","createTime":"2018-10-12T08:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:00:13.000Z","uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50ca931fa559007168eb34a9753058db205ac786","tid":859034,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n洪卓立（Ken）和吳浩康（Deep）兩位好兄弟合作舉辦《他說他的故事》演唱會，Ken的家人和女友湯怡有捧場，感性的他獻唱《回到最愛的那天》已忍不住用紙巾輕輕拭淚，台下有歌迷大叫「唔好喊呀！」作鼓勵，繼續緊接唱《帶著骨灰去旅行》時，他垂下頭泣不成聲。演唱會上，Deep重提Ken多次被傳「死訊」的事，他激動說：「有人死好好笑嗎？試幻想他是你家人父母，唔知會點？」而Ken感慨表示每次傳「死訊」最不開心是父母，因既要擔心他經濟生活，又擔心他得罪人。  Ken完騷後接受訪問，他直言：「我們綵排時看到短片已經眼濕濕，正式上台唱還是激動控制不到，人愈大愈容易喊。事前沒有通知女友，當我唱《骨灰》播短片，她一見到那些一齊去旅行的相，已成功令她喊，畫公仔不需要畫出腸。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20181012/s00009/08726d030006bda71660c29511d6fed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20181012%2Fs00009%2F08726d030006bda71660c29511d6fed1.jpg&h=e2fdb1af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1539330707716&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1539330707716%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181012&d=yJVT0z9mqF5dDCmKlzSFztibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a90a8e95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1539330707716%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181012&h=f6e5eac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1539330707716&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181012</a>"},{"pid":"055a232347ea7985258eca8465229da62f41ef7f","tid":859034,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"貼個咪同張紙巾想點"},{"pid":"23e0f94c1229019e14eb5fd0f036f56861947254","tid":859034,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2